      "module_management": "module purge",
      "environment_setup": [

        "module load openmpi/4.1.1",

        "module list"

      "execution": [
        "./clean",
        "ulimit -s unlimited",
        "nvidia-smi",
        "mpirun -n 1 ./mhd3d.x > MURaM.out"
